{"tid":2301592,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】「釋放海妖」法律文件pdf連結被Twitter列為不安全，轉載有關連結的所有tweet已被BAM！！！","createTime":"2020-11-26T12:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T14:02:03.000Z","uid":88743,"like":212,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"955dad30abc0443eb0b44ba459e2160bdb1730ec","tid":2301592,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:07:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母上上下Twitter click下d link突然間彈呢版野出黎<br />\n之後返返去條link個tweet, 成個唔撚見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aYm0STP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYm0STP.png&h=01c2170d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖條link<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/safety/unsafe_link_warning?unsafe_link=https://defendingtherepublic.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/COMPLAINT-CJ-PEARSON-V.-KEMP-11.25.2020.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsafety%2Funsafe_link_warning%3Funsafe_link%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fdefendingtherepublic.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FCOMPLAINT-CJ-PEARSON-V.-KEMP-11.25.2020.pdf&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=6242d022\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/safety/unsafe_link_warning?unsafe_link=https://defendingtherepublic.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/COMPLAINT-CJ-PEARSON-V.-KEMP-11.25.2020.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\nGoogle Translate:<br />\n根據Twitter的網址政策，Twitter或我們的合作夥伴已將您嘗試訪問的鏈接標識為潛在的垃圾郵件或不安全的鏈接。該鏈接可能屬於以下任何類別：<br />\n<br />\n可能竊取個人信息或損害電子設備的惡意鏈接<br />\n垃圾郵件鏈接會誤導人們或破壞他們的體驗<br />\n可能導致現實世界傷害的暴力或誤導性內容<br />\n某些類別的內容，如果直接發佈在Twitter上，則違反Twitter規則<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「釋放海妖」法律文件pdf連結:<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://defendingtherepublic.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/COMPLAINT-CJ-PEARSON-V.-KEMP-11.25.2020.pdf</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nFYI<br />\n<br />\n[美國大選，釋放海妖］Sidney Powell 已在GA同MI 提出訴訟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2301266\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2301266</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sidneypowell1/status/1331826386449915904?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsidneypowell1%2Fstatus%2F1331826386449915904%3Fs%3D21&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=3967726e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsidneypowell1%2Fstatus%2F1331826386449915904%3Fs%3D21&h=ebd56ba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sidneypowell1/status/1331826386449915904?s=21</a><br />\nTWEET已BAM<br />\n<br />\n所有轉載上面pdf檔連結既TWEET都被BAM<br />\n<br />\n歡迎來到2020審查世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db6d48f1f879f24ae0e603d22935a166dda130f","tid":2301592,"uid":79117,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:08:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c460473e1e1df1d01d78e23bc386d8dd040f89d2","tid":2301592,"uid":79117,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:09:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4e0276dc9f949433f6d06e1951e95e779fc6dde","tid":2301592,"uid":265486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"暴風雨來了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6d35c1d9cac7c6c0383da3fcfff733692a91bb","tid":2301592,"uid":36065,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"ignore this warning and continu