已將您嘗試訪問的鏈接標識為潛在的垃圾郵件或不安全的鏈接。該鏈接可能屬於以下任何類別：<br />\n<br />\n可能竊取個人信息或損害電子設備的惡意鏈接<br />\n垃圾郵件鏈接會誤導人們或破壞他們的體驗<br />\n可能導致現實世界傷害的暴力或誤導性內容<br />\n某些類別的內容，如果直接發佈在Twitter上，則違反Twitter規則<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「釋放海妖」法律文件pdf連結:<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://defendingtherepublic.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/COMPLAINT-CJ-PEARSON-V.-KEMP-11.25.2020.pdf</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nFYI<br />\n<br />\n[美國大選，釋放海妖］Sidney Powell 已在GA同MI 提出訴訟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2301266\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2301266</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sidneypowell1/status/1331826386449915904?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsidneypowell1%2Fstatus%2F1331826386449915904%3Fs%3D21&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=3967726e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsidneypowell1%2Fstatus%2F1331826386449915904%3Fs%3D21&h=ebd56ba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sidneypowell1/status/1331826386449915904?s=21</a><br />\nTWEET已BAM<br />\n<br />\n所有轉載上面pdf檔連結既TWEET都被BAM<br />\n<br />\n歡迎來到2020審查世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:17:10.000Z","msg":"Shitter"},{"pid":"d34871c3b41dfb6e0ac74bf85d590c4d0c0707cb","tid":2301592,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dfcc47d10675ea6df295f6b29522fb29b67eb3","tid":2301592,"uid":130456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"